		<td><b>SNES MASK ROMS</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hi All,
<br />Sorry this is a SNES related question.
<br />
<br />Is it possible to find a generic ROM/PROM that can be programmed and used to replace the SNES Mask ROM in a SNES cartridge?
<br />
<br />I have looked at using EPROMS but it looks a bit messy.
<br />
<br />Thanks for any ideas!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
